  "finger_focus": "Right hand reaches up: 6-7 (index), 8 (middle), 9 (ring), 0 (pinky)",
  "tips": [
    {
      "type": "lead",
      "text": "The left hand owns 1 through 5. Now the right hand takes 6 through 0, and the full number row is yours - every figure for a date, a year, a phone number, a price. This half mirrors the last: the same reach up, the same snap back home, the other hand."
    },
    {
      "type": "drop",
      "text": "6 is the right index, reached up and to the left (it lands between Y and H). 7 is the index too, straight up; 8 the middle; 9 the ring; 0 the pinky, out at the end of the row. One finger climbs to its digit while the rest hold the home row under J K L and the semicolon."
    },
    {
      "type": "callout",
      "icon": "⬆️",
      "title": "Anchor on J",
      "text": "After every digit, bring the index back to J. That one habit keeps the whole hand oriented - lose J and the right hand starts guessing. Reach by feel, return by feel, eyes forward."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "6 7 8 6 7 8 6 7 8 6 7 8 6 7 8",
      "finger": "indigo",
      "title": "Digits 6-7-8",
      "hint": "Index for 6 and 7, middle for 8. Reach up, tap, back to J."
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "9 0 9 0 9 0 9 0 9 0 9 0 9 0 9 0",
      "finger": "pink",
      "title": "Digits 9-0",
      "hint": "Ring for 9, pinky for 0 at the end of the row. Return home each time."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Now all ten digits work together - the kind of mixing real numbers demand, a year, a count, a quick total. Type each group, snap the hand home, and keep your eyes on the line, not the keys."
    },
    {
      "type": "pullquote",
      "text": "A reporter who can type the figures without looking down keeps the thought and the number both. That is the whole game.",
      "by": "Eleanor Hayes, editor"
    },
    {
      "type": "step",
      "kind": "drill",
      "target": "67 89 0 67890 j6 k7 l8 take 6 add 7 see 8 try 9 win 0",
      "finger": "green",
      "title": "The full number row",
      "hint": "Right hand reaches up for each digit and returns to J. One space between groups."
    },
